## Error Handling Guidelines

### 1. Error Type Definition
```rust
#[derive(Debug, thiserror::Error)]
pub enum MyError {
    #[error("IO error: {0}")]
    Io(#[from] std::io::Error),
    #[error("Custom error: {message}")]
